6.2 General GUI Options
=======================

`--pinout-offset-x <num>'
     Horizontal offset of the pin number display. Defaults to `100mil'.

`--pinout-offset-y <num>'
     Vertical offset of the pin number display. Defaults to `100mil'.

`--pinout-text-offset-x <num>'
